<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5532438>
    dc:description "FIGURE 91. Some westernAtlantic Porcellanidae (species reported from Panama) photographed in situ:A, Petrolisthes galathinus (Bosc, 1802) [sensu lato], Tayrona, Colombia; B, C, Porcellana sayana (Leach, 1820), southern Florida, USA [photographs courtesy of Juan-Felipe Lazarus-Agudelo (A) and Linda Ianniello (B, C)]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5532438/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5532416>
    dc:description "FIGURE 83. Porcellana sayana (Leach, 1820): A–C, male (cl 7.7 mm, cw 7.0 mm) from Bocas del Toro, Panama (MZUSP 33471), dorsal (A), ventral (B) and frontal (C) views [photographs by AA]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5532416/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5532420>
    dc:description "FIGURE 85. Porcellana sayana (Leach, 1820):A, extra-limital specimen, male (cl cw indet.) from Florida Bay, USA (FLMNH UF 19582), dorsal view [photograph by AA]; B, extra-limital specimen, male (cl cw indet.) from Florida, USA (FLMNH UF 28581), dorsal view; C, extra-limital specimen, female (cl cw indet.) from Florida, USA (FLMNH UF 28371), dorsal view [photographs in B and C courtesy of Gustav Paulay]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5532420/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5532418>
    dc:description "FIGURE 84. Porcellana sayana (Leach, 1820): A, B, male (cl 7.7 mm, cw 7.0 mm) from Bocas del Toro, Panama (MZUSP 33471), associated with the hermit crab Petrochirus diogenes (Linnaeus) [photographs by AA]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5532418/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

